problem:
In the diagram below, $\|\overrightarrow{OA}\| = 1,$ $\|\overrightarrow{OB}\| = 1,$ and $\|\overrightarrow{OC}\| = \sqrt{2}.$  Also, $\tan \angle AOC = 7$ and $\angle BOC = 45^\circ.$

